      "id": 125,
      "title": "v3.3 [TIER-C] Improve nexus_brief MCP project filter: replace KNOWN_PROJECTS heuristic with store.getAllProjects() metadata-driven match",
      "description": "server/mcp/index.ts nexus_brief handler uses hardcoded KNOWN_PROJECTS list and 'title.includes(project)' heuristic. Misses tasks like 'Fix auth bug' that don't mention 'Nexus' in title. Better: tasks should have an explicit project field, store should expose getAllProjects(), filter on metadata not titles.",
