      "description": "nexus_predict_gaps surfaced these. Decisions referencing deleted features should be marked deprecated or removed. Orphans (#60 claude, #61/#62 general) need typed edges via nexus_link_decisions. Predict suggested 'Add test coverage for usage gauge in sidebar' which is impossible — feature deleted in v3.0-alpha6.",
