    {
      "id": 130,
      "title": "v3.5 [P0] Async ask_overseer — start/poll pattern to survive MCP client timeout",
      "description": "ask_overseer takes 60s+ on local hardware. MCP client timeout is ~60s and progress notifications don't reset it. Fix: split into nexus_ask_overseer_start (returns task_id immediately) + nexus_get_overseer_result (polls for answer). Needs: in-memory task store on server, new route /api/overseer/async, two new MCP tools. Unblocks the entire 200k-context vision (full-codebase analysis, AI predict, weekly digest). Server-side: add /api/overseer/tasks/:id endpoint, store pending/completed states.",
